Therabridge
===========
===========

Lord Victor Cromwell - Believes Nim had his brothers killed. Nim was the only other person who knew about the trip Victor and his brothers were taking, and the attackers seemed to know who the foursome were when they attacked. Thinks Nim wanted Victor's father to bequeath everything to him.

If here first, theives guild, otherwise it's in Huckson.

